# AudioEffectNotchFilter

**Inherits:** [AudioEffectFilter](AudioEffectFilter.md) **\<** [AudioEffect](AudioEffect.md) **\<** [Resource](Resource.md) **\<** [RefCounted](RefCounted.md) **\<** [Object](Object.md)

Adds a notch filter to the Audio bus.

<!-- classref-introduction-group -->

## Description

Attenuates frequencies in a narrow band around the [AudioEffectFilter.cutoff_hz](AudioEffectFilter.md#AudioEffectFilter_property_cutoff_hz) and cuts frequencies outside of this range.
